### Get Saves
GET http://localhost:4000/saves

### Get Saves ?title=xxx
GET http://localhost:4000/saves?title=test

### Get Save By Id
GET http://localhost:4000/saves/1

### Post Save
POST  http://localhost:4000/saves
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Google",
  "url": "https://www.google.com/search?q=test"
}

### Patch Save /:id
PATCH http://localhost:4000/saves/7
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "test patch",
    "url": "https://youtube.com/watch?v=123"
}

### Delete Save /:id
DELETE http://localhost:4000/saves/7
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json